title: Topic 001 Question 039
body: You have a Fabric tenant that contains a warehouse named Warehouse1. Warehouse1 contains a fact table named FactSales that has one billion rows.
You run the following T-SQL statement.
CREATE TABLE test.FactSales AS CLONE OF Dbo.FactSales;
For each of the following statements, select Yes if the statement is true. Otherwise, select No.
NOTE: Each correct selection is worth one point.
